  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the binchotan charcoal grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Slice the scamorza cheese into 8 equal pieces.",
    "Brush the cheese with olive oil and season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Grill the cheese for 2-3 minutes per side, or until lightly charred and melted.",
    "Sprinkle paprika and cumin over the cheese during the last minute of grilling.",
    "Mince the garlic and mix with chopped parsley.",
    "Squeeze lemon juice over the grilled cheese and top with garlic-parsley mixture.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
